name: Lucky Number 8. Classic 8x10 Archival Art Print. Black and White.
description:
★ Number 8 in a curvy rounded type
A classic print that will never go out of style.
Frame it, keep it for yourself, or give it away to someone special!

● Print size: 8x10" (20.3 x 25.4 cm)
● Professionally printed on linen-textured 8.5x11"
(21.6 x 27.9cm) paper using archival inks
● I'll sign it on the back and mail it to you unframed and unmatted in a bend-proof envelope.

Want a different color? Pick your favorite from the color chart and let me know in the Paypal instructions box when you checkout.

★ Also available as a 5x7" (12.7 x 17.8 cm) print.
Email me at coverpage8@gmail.com for more info
